text: Sasheer Zamata Moore (; born May 6, 1986) is an American actress and comedienne. In 2014, she started appearing on Saturday Night Live. She was the first black woman on the show since 2007.https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/snl-hires-sasheer-zamata-first- black-female-cast-member-in-years-20140106 Rolling Stone Zamamta was raised in Indianapolis, Indiana.
